 </table>\n              <p style=\"color:#555555;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;\">\n                An automatic confirmation email was sent to the lead. \n                A follow-up email will go out in 2 hours if they \n                don't respond.\n              </p>\n              <p style=\"color:#888888;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;\n              border-top:1px solid #e0e0e0;padding-top:20px;margin-top:20px;\">\n                Powered by your automated lead system\n              </p>\n            </td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</body>\n</html>",
